    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Hey mind if I seat here?"
            ],
            [
                "Uh, Sure. Go ahead."
            ],
            [
                "......."
            ],
            [
                "The air is suddenly tight, [he] looks a bit frustrated. [he]'s really avoiding eye contact."
            ],
            [
                "Well, uh.. what's your name?"
            ],
            [
                "My name? Why you... Uh, name's Victor. Sorry."
            ],
            [
                "That sounded rude, didn't meant to. It's just..."
            ],
            [
                "You seem a bit stressed, are you okay?"
            ],
            [
                "Yah, completely fine really. For now."
            ],
            [
                "Well, I'm trying to hide from my boss right now. So as long she doesn't catch me."
            ],
            [
                "She's supper pissed."
            ],
            [
                "That explains the uniform and the lack of nametag."
            ],
            [
                "Why are you here? Hidin' from your boss too?"
            ],
            [
                "I came here... to the speed dating event."
            ],
            [
                "All this was a speed dating event? Oh so that explains the hearts and the corny decoration."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, why is your boss so pissed?"
            ],
            [
                "Let's leave it at me making a little mistake."
            ],
            [
                "A little mistake?"
            ],
            [
                "Well, big mistake. Bad one, might've made her loose a bit of money."
            ],
            [
                "Let's just say that maybe I might have MAYBE left the espresso machine build up too much steam pressure."
            ],
            [
                "So you are saying it exploded?"
            ],
            [
                "It just malfunctioned alright? Oh Crap! IT'S HER!"
            ],
            [
                "Victor hid down under the table. I can feel Victor barely fitting down the table."
            ],
            [
                "What are you doing? HEY? What the-"
            ],
            [
                "Uh, I don't know, you just scared me, and got under the table. It's like instinct or something."
            ],
            [
                "GET OUT OF HERE FREAK"
            ],
            [
                "No NO, WAIT, IT'S NOT WHAT YOU THINK. I REALLY JUST GOTTA HIDE."
            ],
            [
                "Victor is trying to yell as loudly as he can with whispers, desperately."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, I swear, please... Don't make any sound. She'll kill me, please.. I implore you, please. shhh, just..."
            ],
            [
                "Not touching or seeing anything I swear, please. don't rat me up, please dude!"
            ],
            [
                "...... You know what?......"
            ],
            [
                "I'm kinda feeling like screaming"
            ],
            [
                "WAIT, HOLD IT! PLEASE DUDE, YOU DON'T KNOW HOW SHE IS, SHE REAL BAD. COME HELP ME OUT PLEASE. BE HAVE MERCY."
            ],
            [
                "NOT A PERVERT, I swear. please, believe me. You got no idea who you playing with."
            ],
            [
                "Can't stop messing up can't you? You do not make good first impressions."
            ],
            [
                "Alright, sure fine! I'll give you something you want. what is it, whatever you wish, I swear! Just cover me up on this one please."
            ]
